modules.suffixTree

Class NodePosition

  • java.lang.Object
    • modules.suffixTree.NodePosition
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparable<NodePosition>

    public class NodePosition
extends Object
implements Comparable<NodePosition>
    A simple POJO for the positions of nodes in a suffix tree. Implements Comparable as well as overrides equals() and hashCode() to work in sets, trees etc. based on it's values instead of by object identity.

      • compareTo

        public int compareTo(NodePosition o)
        A NodePosition is smaller/greater than another if any of it's values is smaller/greter than the others. Vlues are checked in the order: typeContextNr, textNr, star, end If any of those is smaller/greater, the appropriate result is returned.
